  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Reflexology treatment may influence the severity of chemotherapy-induced nausea and vomiting.
      This study aims to investigate the clinical effect of reflexology on chemotherapy-induced
      nausea and vomiting.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
